<item>
            <title>[LU-14482] MDTs added after OST Pool create don&apos;t show pools</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14482</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Steps to reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Create Lustre FS with some MDTs and some OST Pools&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Extend said FS with more MDTs and OSTs&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add some of the new OSTs to existing pools (may not be neccissary)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;check the pools on one of the new MDTs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Expect:&lt;br/&gt;
 see list of OSTs in pool&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Actually:&lt;br/&gt;
 No pools listed on new MDTs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Workaround:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Destroy and recreate pools&lt;/p&gt;</description>
